@octopuspaul42 predicts the future or answers any question. It is the Twitter version of Paul The Octopus. It predicts using a complex algorithm involving Number 42. 

Just Follow and reply to @octopuspaul42 with your options in boxes [...]

Example:

John: Hey @octopuspaul42. When will i win the lottery? [Today] [Friday the 13th] [Birthday]
octopuspaul42: @John: Birthday
